# Contributing

Thank you for considering contributing to the Hydro smart contracts!

Contributing to this repo can mean many things such as participating in
discussion or proposing code changes.

Hydro has many stakeholders and holds user funds, so we take security and
user experience very seriously. We particularly appreciate contributions that help us
improve these aspects of the project.

When contributing, please create a new branch for your contribution and submit a pull request.
Please include a description of your changes and the problem you are solving.
We cannot accept pull requests without a clear problem statement and description,
as it is important for us to understand the purpose of the change.